fields.title: Physics
fields.description: Explore the fascinating world of physics with our courses! Whether you're a beginner or have some prior knowledge, we offer engaging lessons to help you understand the fundamental principles of the universe. From motion to energy, light to sound, our courses make physics fun and accessible for everyone. Join us and start unraveling the mysteries of the natural world today!

fields.title: Art
fields.description: Unleash your creativity with our art courses! Whether you're a budding artist or just looking to explore your creative side, we offer a range of courses to suit your interests. From drawing and painting to sculpture and digital art, dive into various mediums and techniques. Our courses are designed to inspire and nurture your artistic talent, no matter your skill level. Join us and embark on a journey of self-expression and discovery through the world of art!

fields.title: Business
fields.description: Ready to take on the world of business? Our courses cover everything from entrepreneurship to finance, marketing to management. Whether you're starting your own venture or climbing the corporate ladder, we've got you covered. Gain practical skills, insights, and strategies to succeed in today's dynamic business landscape. Explore our courses and kickstart your business journey today!

fields.title: Information Technology (IT)
fields.description: Step into the world of tech with our IT courses! Whether you're a beginner or an expert, we've got something for everyone. Learn coding, cybersecurity, data science, and more. Get ready to boost your skills and thrive in the digital world! Start exploring now!

fields.title: Language
fields.description: Discover the world through words! Our language courses offer a passport to new cultures, friendships, and opportunities. From practical conversation skills to deep dives into literature and culture, explore a diverse array of languages tailored to your interests and goals. Start your language learning journey today!

fields.title: Assignment in python
fields.description: This is an assignment in python that you have to answer.

fields.title: Impacts of Technology
fields.description:
Provide an introduction, body, and conclusion.
Discuss both positive and negative impacts of technology.
Use clear and concise language.
Ensure proper citations for external sources.
Original work only; plagiarism will not be tolerated.
Feedback: You will receive feedback within two weeks.

Requirements:
Essay length: Approximately 500-700 words.
Submission: Upload your essay as a PDF file.
